nnoremap <F12> :tabnext<CR>
inoremap <F12> <Esc>:tabnext<CR>
" Cycle tabs (reverse)
nnoremap <silent> \tp :tabprevious<CR>
nnoremap <F11> :tabprevious<CR>
inoremap <F11> <Esc>:tabprevious<CR>
" }}}
